<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Liegeman" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Liegeman,</orth> vassal, subject: <cit><quote>swore the devil his true l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.372" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 372</bibl></cit>. With <emph>to</emph>: <cit><quote>as thou art l. to us,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 2.3.174" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 3, 174</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>true liegemen to his crown,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.128" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 4, 128</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.1.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 1, 15</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>